      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It sounds like you're experiencing a deep sense of disconnection with your past self, which can be common during significant life transitions. Sometimes acknowledging these feelings can help reconnect you with aspects of your identity you may have repressed or ignored. It might be helpful to consider talking with someone you trust about where this strange emptiness is coming from.",
      "source": "target",
